data.name: label3.Text
data.value: [Ctrl+W] Analyze grid, then form a word [Ctrl+E] Analyze grid and add all its letters to DB as unknowns [Ctrl+N] Form a word [Ctrl+M] Form next word (disabled) [Ctrl+R] Learn all unknowns in the grid [UP] Learn this screenpart as YES [DOWN] Learn this screenpart as NO [BACKSPACE] Forget all screenparts from this [Ctrl+Q] Toggle Autonomous mode [Ctrl+Shift+A/S/L/P/U] Capture Attack/Scramble/Life/Power/Purify [NumPad1-5] Heart "3" is 0/0.25/0.5/0.75/1 [NumPad9] Clear all saved Heart screenparts [Ctrl+Shift+X] Remove this word from DB

data.name: label15.Text
data.value:
[Alt+R] Remember all unknown letters in the grid as 'unassigned'. You will assign letters to them later. [Alt+Shift+R] Remember ALL letters in the grid as 'unassigned'. You will assign letters to them later.
[Alt+L] Enter or exit "targeted recognition (lock) mode" While in lock mode: [NumPad] move targeting reticle [NumPad 5] Remember the target letter [NumPad 0] Remember and store the target letter with its best guess
